phrases: We are doing a fall festival!
Title The God, going to hot spring”
The Deity Goes to the Beach
The Deity, going to hot spring
If you touch it, you will be blessed.
A tired girl starts her day
With a sigh like the moan of a violin
A cherry bursts in her mouth
This was before we had met
This is the first time I have ever felt like this
I could see that your pretty eyes were filled with contempt
But I had to go home
Even at the bus stop, you gave me the cold shoulder
The fireworks in the sky pulse
I would like to be a naughty girl
I am tired of being good
It is for a good reason
So let me be bad for once
It looks like Saturday is going to be sunny
tameiki wa bioron no shirabe ni nite
manazashi wa aku no hana sakimidarete mo
basu sutoppu demo anata wa tsurenai
Momozono Nanami's father ran away from home after losing all of his money on gambling.
She was evicted, and some weird occurrences later, she became a deity.
She then fell in love with her familiar, the demon fox, Tomoe.
They even went out on dates.
Though later she got dumped and felt very depressed.
And on a trip to the beach, Tomoe was imprisoned under the sea.
She went all the way to the Dragon Palace to rescue him and started to feel good again.
She even traveled back in time,
but Tomoe was a super scary villain!
However, her love for him never changed.
Then she defeated the Earth Spider and purified the Mikaga Shrine from the miasma.
Their relationship became more passionate and intense.
Now, you must be wondering what happened next, right?
I have been kind of restless lately.
These are the real flying legs!
Can we formalize the familiar contract?
From the bottom of my heart.
But now I feel like I am needed.
For now, this is good enough.
Tomoe, do we have something sweet to eat?
We have some sweet potato cake, right?
What you wanted is inside this box, Tomoe-sama.
Thank you for your hard work, Tanuko.
I guess I do not need Nanami any more.
I cannot stand how selfish and annoying she can be.
Thank you for all the hard work you did, but I do not need you any longer!
You just lured, used, and discarded me.
A lady in this kind of show always gets tricked.
You do not like your red bean jelly?
Nanami-chan, I do not think it is poisoned.
Tomoe, you really think you do not need me?
Red bean jelly is tasty all right, but I want to eat something soothing.
Oh, that is the box Tanuko-san brought.
I wonder what is in it.
Just eat your red bean jelly!
I am sure there is something in it he does not want me to see.
I, the super star Kurama-sama, bought some expensive crabs for you, poor people.
I guess you do not have anyone to eat hotpot with.
You still do not feel like eating?
You are always bothering me with talk about eels and crabs.
Mizuki, do not pour her sake.
She is not allowed to drink.
Then it is only for us.
Everyone knows I am a heavy drinker!
He is just trying to lie.
Do not you want to hear some of my awesome stories?
What do you mean stupid, you moron!
In that case, why do not you guys see who can drink the most?
We have a lot of sake in Mizuki's brewery.
The person who passes out first will be the loser.
Pour, pour, pour, pour, and pour!
Pour, pour, pour, pour, and pour!
I will see what is inside the box!
I did not know he thinks of me like that.
I kind of knew, but I was still depending on his can-do-anything wizard-like skills.
I will not randomly tell him that I want to eat purple yum and chestnut cake ever again.
I did not notice until it was too late.
The secret weapon that makes Tomoe think I am useless.
We heard Tomoe-sama was looking for some pears, so we gave him the best ones we could find.
You told him you wanted a pear tart.
You cannot tell her that, Tanuko!
He said to keep it a secret,
because it would embarrassing if he cannot bake it right.
At a time like this, a pear tart would be nice!
I cannot stand how selfish and annoying she can be.
TL note: Yonashi can mean pears and useless at the same time.
You are the only person who can speak to him freely.
Even if he acts cold or mean, he is always looking out for me, and that makes me happy.
I will pretend I did not see inside the box.
She does not have those watermelon breasts.
She may not look it, but she is pretty chubby.
Padding their bras so their breasts look bigger.
They would look way bigger if she was doing that!
Even with pads, she would not look big.
There were no pads in there!
Give it to me more, Nanami-chan.
Well, we should go somewhere far away and relax.
Mikage Shrine does not have holidays.
Where do you want to go?
If Mizuki can watch the shrine, I guess we can take a one-day trip.
Somebody has to be at the shrine, and I have to protect Nanami.
are not you spoiling Nanami-chan a little too much lately?
Well, you are practically taking her place at school, and you got pears to make her a tart.
Maybe it is because you are a good familiar,
but if you keep on doing that, she will become a deity that cannot do anything on her own.
She is going to become an empty-headed fool who cannot do anything?
Not as long as I am her familiar.
Nanami, this is just a one-day trip, right?
You look like you plan to stay for a few months.
I brought all of this so he will not have to lift a finger.
I need this just in case!
That is heavy, is not it?
I have to show him I can carry this by myself.
Or he will get tired of me.
Nanami, is not that the bus to the hotel?
If you would like to go to the hotel, please ride this bus!
I guess this is another way to get there.
Must be a nice hotel, since I chose it!
I came here with Kotaro for the hot springs.
Then we can enjoy the hot spring together.
That is good, becuse I cannot be in there with Tomoe!
That is good for you too, Tomoe!
You will have Kotaro-kun to keep you company.
Are you guys going to Koiiwa too?
There is a rock called Koiiwa.
If you touch it with your partner...
Kotaro heard of it from the female customers.
Kotaro is working part-time at the sweets shop.
We would planned to come this hot springs anyway, and I heard that it was sort of the spot for...
I will tighten my bonds with him.
I am not going to that superstitious place.
While you are wasting time there, I will be enjoying the hot springs.
It will not work if we do not touch the rock together, so we are going.
We came all the way here, so we are going.
The hot springs will feel better after some exercise, so we are going.
Please keep an eye on our lugggage!
Koiiwa is just a short walk from the hotel.
I guess we will follow it.
The slope is not that steep, so a mile should not be a lot of work.
Tomoe, I wonder what Koiiwa looks like!
So you ended up bringing that big bag?
Look, I brought snacks and stuff just in case.
Let us eat once we get there.
So if we get tired, we can have a snack midway.
I am well prepared, are not I?
Thank goodness I worked so hard.
This is starting to look like a mountain path.
There is a root over there.
I am glad those two are doing well.
I am as good as it gets.
If you keep grabbing my hands like this, then I will want to climb even more.
It is getting steeper, so be careful.
Will you make it there in those shoes?
Yeah, they are perfect for this.
I left my sneakers in my other bag.
I am all right, I am telling you!
If I let him help me now, he will think I am useless again.
Are not you pushing yourself too hard today?
Let us go quickly and touch Koiiwa.
The signs says ten more meters.
There is a very steep cliff in front of them.
Do we have to climb this?
You cannot do it in that outfit.
I can use this and climb up, right?
Do you really have to do all that?
We came here for hot springs!
There is no need to go to such a remote place.
I want to touch Koiiwa with you and have an eternal bond!
I will help you from down here.
As long as I am her familiar...
I do not want to disappoint him.
I want to take his hand, but...
I wanted to walk with Tomoe while holding hands, but...
You are finally holding my hand.
Even if we do not touch a stupid rock, I will be next to you forevermore.
If you could do everything by yourself, I would not have a reason to exist.
On my own, I am useless.
But when I am with Tomoe, the world is my oyster.
You were fighting with your familiar earlier, but you made peace, right?
It was not that big a deal.
He feels strongly about you, you know.
and we are deity and familiar.
I hope I can be with Tomoe forever and ever.
No conversation in the men's hot spring.
Local specialty: hot springs and sake!
Otohiko, I cannot see the moon at all.
Why do not you take your glasses off?
The fox becoming a familiar is funny enough as it is,
but to be working for a human girl?
While I was not here, he became a big sissy.
I will make you remember what you used to be.
THE DEITY, GOING TO A HOT SPRING
